#Format is: minute hour dayofmonth month dayofweek
# * * * * * *
# | | | | | |
# | | | | | +-- Year              (range: 1900-3000)
# | | | | +---- Day of the Week   (range: 0-6, 0 for Sunday, 1 for Monday, 6 for Saturday)
# | | | +------ Month of the Year (range: 1-12)
# | | +-------- Day of the Month  (range: 1-31)
# | +---------- Hour              (range: 0-23)
